Body: Description: The server returned a "500 Internal Server Error".

Internal:

Please re-run the 2 commands in screen:

 

mailer was cleared + shadows and UI is accessible now
the disk space was cleared, but the e-mail alerts are still not being sent
What We've Learned Updated: The disk space of the EPP Server got filled up with e-mail alerts which were not being sent because their email server settings were modified.
Next Steps Updated: A remote session was set in order to help them to configure the e-mail server settings.
